        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 9 at 10:02PM EDT by NWS Northern Indiana</headline>
        <description>Recent observations across extreme northern Indiana and lower
Michigan suggest snow showers will continue across the area, with
rain farther south. A recent observer measurement reported 2
inches of snowfall in Hillsdale County Michigan.

Drivers are urged to use additional caution if driving on the
roads tonight. Slow down and allow extra space between you and
the vehicle in front of you.
</description>
